us aspects of Jaubert’s work on early Christian and Jewish calendars, including her solution to an old problem of the conflicting chronologies for the Passion Week in the Synoptic Gospels and the Gospel of John. The volume also contains the complete bibliography of Jaubert’s scholarly works and a biographical sketch of her life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh1 aAndersen, Francis I., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaucham, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeckwith, Roger T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDorival, Gilles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLourié, Basile, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOrlov, Andrei, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOrlov, Andrei, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPetit, Madeleine, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRay, Walter D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVanderKam, James C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 avan Esbroeck, Michel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2015z978311066303740uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146321541540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463215415423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463215415/original  a978-3-11-066303-7  Gorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2015c2001d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_E